commit.message:
rs6000-builtin.def: Correct pasto error for stxvd2x and stxvw4x built-in functions.

2016-04-25  Bill Schmidt  <wschmidt@linux.vnet.ibm.com>

	* rs6000-builtin.def: Correct pasto error for stxvd2x and stxvw4x
	built-in functions.

From-SVN: r235412
